，割地賠款」等字眼。有教育學者質疑前者說法並無任何證據，後者更鼓動師生仇恨外國，批評東華三院「跟足政權口吻」表忠。<br />\n<br />\n東華三院早前向屬校派發《國安教育參考資源套》，長逾百頁，由教育科主管吳奇壎任顧問，列出從憲制、法律、執行等不同角度的問與答。<br />\n<br />\n其中一問「成立《國安法》對香港社會有何逼切性？」的答案提及，過去香港發生的事件「並非只是社會運動，不法分子企圖分裂國家、顛覆政權、進行恐怖活動，也有外部勢力的干預」，更指香港沒有法例防範、制止和懲治，故「中央政府有逼切性作出決定」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210414/H4RWD65GTVAYPKU5HSQXYNCXTI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210414%2FH4RWD65GTVAYPKU5HSQXYNCXTI%2F&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11JgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=5adf54aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210414%2FH4RWD65GTVAYPKU5HSQXYNCXTI%2F&h=a23ca9a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210414/H4RWD65GTVAYPKU5HSQXYNCXTI/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T23:45:44.000Z","msg":"成個清朝得億幾人，死3億人邊度黎？<br />\n我淨係知大平天國戰爭死左7000萬人"},{"pid":"d5ea4f628eb0d1858446bdee62e6b4a7878307e2","tid":2487710,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T23:57:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"856891b29a0c77eec622d7ce4be629630bb010cd","tid":2487710,"uid":362015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T00:03:25.000Z","msg":"拎番海參威未？"},{"pid":"d1dfeb97b676637a8ae3c25eb79b7ccfe682b500","tid":2487710,"uid":237300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T00:12:31.000Z","msg":"東張又要訪問黃智賢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfa7bb0697ba3e9af6009eba7d9ec488fef514d3","tid":2487710,"uid":57205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T00:14:12.000Z","msg":"毛主席講過槍杆子出政權<br />\n係咪想話毛主席係恐怖份子"},{"pid":"488b5ae42311381f9554909a49a6d4da1e77d696","tid":2487710,"uid":3457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T00:14:28.000Z","msg":"岩呀 再播721 d片比小朋友睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/